-- Teck’s CEO Lindsay Says It Won’t Be Iron-Ore Project Developer
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   D o n v i l l e
-- 2012-05-08T19:20:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-08/teck-s-ceo-lindsay-says-it-won-t-be-iron-ore-project-developer.html
Teck Resources Ltd. (TCK/B)  is interested in
entering the iron-ore industry and would seek to acquire a
producing asset rather than develop a mining project, Chief
Executive Officer Don Lindsay said.  Lindsay spoke today at Bloomberg’s Canada Economic Summit
in Toronto.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christopher Donville in Vancouver at 
